title: I GIVE ALL TO YOU
bible_ref: Offer yourselves to God, as those who have been brought from death to life. Romans 6:13
verses: I give all my service to You,=I give all my service to You;=No matter the cost or what others do,=I give all my service to You.
I give all my future to You,=I give all my future to You;=No matter the cost or what others do,=I give all my future to You.
I give all my worship to You,=I give all my worship to You;=No matter the cost or what others do,=I give all my worship to You.
